1288
01:21:32,440 --> 01:21:34,266
I never could face her.

1289
01:21:34,362 --> 01:21:37,336
I felt I was party to it.
We were all party to it.

1290
01:21:37,432 --> 01:21:40,537
If only I had said,

1291
01:21:40,633 --> 01:21:42,680
"Don't go, Donald. It's crazy."

1292
01:21:42,776 --> 01:21:44,759
I should have said that.

1293
01:21:44,855 --> 01:21:47,766
He made the wrong decisions.

1294
01:21:47,862 --> 01:21:50,619
In a way, he turned
the initial difficulties

1295
01:21:50,715 --> 01:21:52,409
into something much worse...

1296
01:21:52,505 --> 01:21:55,409
into a disaster for himself
and for the rest of us.

1297
01:21:57,466 --> 01:21:59,478
But he was trying
to do the best he could

1298
01:21:59,574 --> 01:22:01,619
to get back to us.

1299
01:22:04,602 --> 01:22:08,825
And that's all he could do, really.

1300
01:22:10,298 --> 01:22:12,823
Everything angered me at that time.

1301
01:22:12,919 --> 01:22:14,617
Anger just boiled over.

1302
01:22:14,713 --> 01:22:17,272
And I blamed everyone

1303
01:22:17,368 --> 01:22:19,094
and everything.

1304
01:22:20,347 --> 01:22:22,936
I feel that I failed.

1305
01:22:23,032 --> 01:22:25,975
I didn't stop him from going

1306
01:22:26,070 --> 01:22:29,043
and I didn't help him
when he needed it.

1307
01:22:32,763 --> 01:22:34,873
But people need to dream.

1308
01:22:34,968 --> 01:22:38,872
I think Donald needed that,

1309
01:22:38,968 --> 01:22:41,656
and he had a right to have it.

1310
01:22:44,699 --> 01:22:48,119
The crowd criticized him.

1311
01:22:48,215 --> 01:22:51,321
The crowd mocked him.

1312
01:22:51,417 --> 01:22:53,939
And I didn't want that to happen.

1313
01:23:00,091 --> 01:23:03,192
When somebody has risked

1314
01:23:03,288 --> 01:23:05,498
and failed,

1315
01:23:05,593 --> 01:23:07,898
and when somebody has fallen

1316
01:23:07,994 --> 01:23:11,253
from the tightrope
they've been walking on,

1317
01:23:11,349 --> 01:23:14,231
somebody has to pick them up

1318
01:23:14,327 --> 01:23:16,535
and give them a burial.

1319
01:23:19,515 --> 01:23:22,232
The best thing is that
a friend should do that.

1320
01:23:23,995 --> 01:23:27,639
Don wanted to make
a success of his life.

1321
01:23:29,178 --> 01:23:31,514
He just wanted to see

1322
01:23:31,610 --> 01:23:34,902
a bright future for himself

1323
01:23:34,998 --> 01:23:36,945
and his family.

1324
01:23:42,299 --> 01:23:44,759
In my mind,

1325
01:23:44,855 --> 01:23:48,538
I gave him a hero's...

1326
01:23:48,634 --> 01:23:50,427
burial.

